1
00:00:02,400 --> 00:00:06,500
<i>Coffee, Do Me a Favor</i>

2
00:00:08,130 --> 00:00:10,860
<i>Yong Jun Hyung</i>

3
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:13,730
<i>Kim Min Young</i>

4
00:00:13,730 --> 00:00:17,000
<i>Chae Seo Jin</i>

5
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:19,380
<i>Lee Tae Ri — Gil Eun Hye</i>

6
00:00:19,380 --> 00:00:21,580
<i>Kim Neul Me — Ryu Hye Rin — Maeng Se Chang — Han Jae Hoo</i>

7
00:00:23,310 --> 00:00:27,060
♫ <i>With a pretty hairdo and eye-catching lipstick</i> ♫

8
00:00:27,060 --> 00:00:32,890
♫ <i>I wear clothes that I saved for a special day to go out</i> ♫

9
00:00:32,890 --> 00:00:36,080
<i>Final Episode</i>

10
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:58,370
<i>- Oh Go Woon is Lee Seul Bi.
- What?</i>

11
00:00:58,370 --> 00:01:01,710
<i>Oh Go Woon is Lee Seul Bi and Lee Seul Bi is Oh Go Woon.</i>

12
00:01:01,710 --> 00:01:05,710
<i>Oh Go Woon never existed in the first place.</i>

13
00:01:05,710 --> 00:01:07,510
<i>What's with that bandage? </i>

14
00:01:07,510 --> 00:01:14,080
<i>This is... like a promise I made to myself that I won't let go of the pen</i>

15
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:18,900
<i>until I'm satisfied with my drawings. It's kind of like that. </i>

16
00:01:18,900 --> 00:01:23,550
<i>That's amusing. Seul Bi also had the same sort of habit like that. </i>

17
00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:28,730
<i>They say best friends have similar moods and habits.</i>

18
00:01:39,710 --> 00:01:42,880
<i>Writer Im... I</i>

19
00:01:48,740 --> 00:01:50,340
<i>Jjang-gu Appa</i>

20
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:06,730
<i>I left early because I was tired, Writer Im.</i>

21
00:02:06,730 --> 00:02:10,710
<i>I will definitely tell you tomorrow what I was planning on telling you today.</i>

22
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:14,680
<i>Be careful on your way home. I had fun today.</i>

23
00:02:36,670 --> 00:02:40,640
Thank you.

24
00:02:42,990 --> 00:02:46,060
Why did I get off here?

25
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:49,040
I don't even know anymore.

26
00:02:49,830 --> 00:02:54,140
♫ Because the earth is round ♫

27
00:02:54,140 --> 00:02:58,160
♫ As I keep walking, ♫

28
00:02:58,160 --> 00:03:05,530
♫ I will get to meet all Lee Seul Bi's in the world ♫

29
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:26,910
You seem like you're awake, so please open your eyes.

30
00:03:32,090 --> 00:03:34,240
My head...

31
00:03:35,030 --> 00:03:36,890
Is there something wrong?

32
00:03:36,890 --> 00:03:39,740
Ah, it seems like you fainted because you were shocked.

33
00:03:39,740 --> 00:03:43,230
Your head hurting right now is caused by your alcohol intake.

34
00:03:43,230 --> 00:03:45,510
Ah... yes.

35
00:03:45,510 --> 00:03:48,200
Your guardian will be here soon.

36
00:03:56,340 --> 00:04:00,150
I am fine now. You can leave.

37
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:04,600
The doctor said to use up all that IV fluid before leaving. Just rest a little bit more.

38
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:12,510
Here. Drink this.

39
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:48,870
Stop it. It's annoying.

40
00:04:48,870 --> 00:04:53,500
- What?
- I'm saying, you pretending to be pondering about things is annoying.

41
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:05,350
Hey. How can you say it like that?

42
00:05:05,350 --> 00:05:08,730
Every day you're like, "I'll tell him today. I'll tell him tomorrow."

43
00:05:08,730 --> 00:05:12,970
You keep delaying it, and enjoying yourself in the end.

44
00:05:14,090 --> 00:05:18,640
Don't you think it's time to stop pretending to be pretty and nice?

45
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:21,080
Hey. Park Ah Reum.

46
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:26,350
Honestly, you're really happy right now.

47
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:29,550
You're dating your first love and you work together.

48
00:05:29,550 --> 00:05:32,060
You got to fit into all the clothes you couldn't fit into before.

49
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:34,810
Everyone around you tells you that you're pretty all the time.

50
00:05:34,810 --> 00:05:38,290
Wow. Just how nice is that?

51
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:46,970
Are you being like that to me right now because you are jealous of me?

52
00:05:46,970 --> 00:05:51,350
Yeah. I feel jealous and I'm annoyed.

53
00:05:51,350 --> 00:05:55,130
Sure, you had enough of living as Oh Go Woon.

54
00:05:55,130 --> 00:05:57,810
Even so, does that mean Lee Seul Bi is going to go anywhere?

55
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:06,240
Fine. I'm sorry.

56
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:10,260
For pretending to ponder about something too much.

57
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:43,620
Seul Bi! Seul Bi!

58
00:06:46,250 --> 00:06:48,520
Ahjussi...

59
00:06:49,490 --> 00:06:52,060
Everything is messed up.

60
00:06:52,060 --> 00:06:55,600
We all are messed up.

61
00:06:56,970 --> 00:07:00,850
But I can't let it be.

62
00:07:04,570 --> 00:07:11,660
I... won't drink any more coffee from today onward.

63
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:13,650
You won't drink it?

64
00:07:14,470 --> 00:07:21,310
I can't... be like this forever.

65
00:07:22,010 --> 00:07:28,060
Is that so? I thought you never wanted to return back to your original appearance,

66
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:31,750
so I came up with a very powerful coffee.

67
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:40,600
What... are you talking about?

68
00:07:44,580 --> 00:07:48,690
If you drink this, you no longer need to fight against time.

69
00:07:48,690 --> 00:07:51,990
Whatever you eat, you don't need to worry about gaining weight.

70
00:07:51,990 --> 00:07:57,280
It's a coffee that allows you to live as Oh Go Woon forever.

71
00:07:57,280 --> 00:08:04,650
<i>If I don't drink this coffee, I will go back to how it was in the past.</i>

72
00:08:04,650 --> 00:08:07,630
<i>If you let this girl sit here, how do you expect me to breathe?!</i>

73
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:09,960
<i>However, don't treat her too nicely, Writer Im.</i>

74
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:14,060
<i>Those types of girls will misunderstand your kindness and think that you like them.</i>

75
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:17,150
<i>You should draw a line in advance.</i>

76
00:08:39,020 --> 00:08:42,270
<i>She is fat. It's true, but...</i>

77
00:09:37,500 --> 00:09:39,260
Seul Bi...

78
00:09:46,730 --> 00:09:52,900
<i>Subtitles brought to you by the Coffee Please team @viki.com</i>

79
00:09:53,390 --> 00:09:55,320
I wasn't...

80
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:58,700
able to sleep one bit last night.

81
00:09:59,850 --> 00:10:03,140
Even when I heard Ye Na's words,

82
00:10:03,140 --> 00:10:06,420
I thought she was just saying nonsense.

83
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:16,750
At first...

84
00:10:18,860 --> 00:10:22,950
I also didn't believe it.

85
00:10:22,950 --> 00:10:26,910
However, after I drank that coffee,

86
00:10:26,910 --> 00:10:31,770
I really experienced a change.

87
00:10:35,710 --> 00:10:39,830
At first, I knew I should've stopped,

88
00:10:41,010 --> 00:10:44,120
but after time passed,

89
00:10:45,710 --> 00:10:49,980
Go Woon really felt like me.

90
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:58,950
Lee Seul Bi seemed fake to me. That's what happened.

91
00:11:02,420 --> 00:11:05,640
I really feel like my head is about to explode.

92
00:11:08,970 --> 00:11:11,990
During all those time, whom was I dating?

93
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:16,410
Whom did I like?

94
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:20,150
Everything was me.

95
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:26,760
Although the outside appearance was different, but the one who liked you and spent time with you

96
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:29,170
was really me.

97
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:32,470
Why did you deceive me?

98
00:11:34,250 --> 00:11:36,600
Just why did you do that?

99
00:11:38,450 --> 00:11:43,480
Do you still not know?

100
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,580
No, I don't know.

101
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:54,370
I really don't know the reason why you had to completely change your outside appearance in order to trick me.

102
00:11:59,530 --> 00:12:01,930
It was because of you.

103
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:09,860
It was because you finally started to accept me.

104
00:12:10,770 --> 00:12:12,410
What?

105
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:22,290
I have been by your side all this time,

106
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:27,080
but you never saw me as a woman.

107
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:29,480
However,

108
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:35,610
you, who never accepted me when I was in my original appearance,

109
00:12:36,950 --> 00:12:41,940
when I was Oh Go Woon, you accepted me!

110
00:12:49,130 --> 00:12:51,890
I really don't know

111
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:56,030
what is what.

112
00:13:39,250 --> 00:13:41,550
Why is there nothing here?

113
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:56,250
<i>Sticky</i>

114
00:13:56,870 --> 00:13:59,390
<i>The number you have dialed does not exist.</i>

115
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:03,020
<i>Please double check the number that was dialed.</i>

116
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:08,010
Excuse me, is Jeong Won not here?

117
00:14:08,010 --> 00:14:09,820
Didn't you hear?

118
00:14:09,820 --> 00:14:13,370
- He quit last night.
- Pardon?!

119
00:14:14,780 --> 00:14:16,910
He never told me that.

120
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:21,540
That's strange. I thought you'd be the first person he would tell.

121
00:14:26,490 --> 00:14:29,410
I shouldn't have ever drunk that coffee.

122
00:14:29,970 --> 00:14:32,790
If it wasn't for that coffee,

123
00:14:34,220 --> 00:14:37,000
I would be able to stay next to Writer.

124
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:41,560
Why did you do that to me?

125
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:43,770
You did it on purpose, right?

126
00:14:43,770 --> 00:14:47,830
You gave me a pretty face and it made me greedy.

127
00:14:47,830 --> 00:14:49,420
You were messing around with me, right?

128
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:51,670
Am I wrong?!

129
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:55,940
You don't even deserve the title of a god.

130
00:14:55,940 --> 00:14:58,830
You're just a mere scammer!

131
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:03,340
The one that chose that coffee

132
00:15:05,470 --> 00:15:09,420
was Seul Bi, which is you.

133
00:15:23,090 --> 00:15:28,550
♫ <i>I am looking at you</i> ♫

134
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:34,320
♫ <i>for a long time from a distance</i> ♫

135
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:37,250
♫ <i>My day is ending</i> ♫

136
00:15:37,250 --> 00:15:40,870
♫ <i>My day is ending</i> ♫

137
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:46,090
♫ <i>and I am only thinking of you</i> ♫

138
00:15:46,090 --> 00:15:51,920
♫ <i>Those small moments are</i> ♫

139
00:15:51,920 --> 00:15:57,780
♫ <i>like fluttering memories</i> ♫

140
00:15:57,780 --> 00:16:00,810
♫ <i>They flow </i> ♫

141
00:16:00,810 --> 00:16:06,190
♫ <i>around you</i> ♫

142
00:16:06,190 --> 00:16:10,180
♫ <i>like dream</i> ♫

143
00:16:10,180 --> 00:16:14,190
♫ <i>Without anyone noticing,</i> ♫

144
00:16:14,190 --> 00:16:18,710
♫ <i>my feeling grew and grew</i> ♫

145
00:16:18,710 --> 00:16:24,120
♫ <i>I have been hiding it deep inside</i> ♫

146
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:29,280
♫ <i>and I felt asleep</i> ♫

147
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:43,450
Hey, Hyeon Woo. You're going to catch a cold.

148
00:16:43,450 --> 00:16:45,830
You knew everything, right?

149
00:16:48,770 --> 00:16:50,610
I'm sorry.

150
00:16:54,510 --> 00:17:00,130
I trust in you. You should've told me!

151
00:17:00,130 --> 00:17:04,960
It's was because it was really strange.

152
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:08,400
I also wasn't sure how to tell you.

153
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:10,290
Plus, Go Woon— I mean,

154
00:17:12,070 --> 00:17:16,750
Seul Bi told me she would tell you herself.

155
00:17:20,380 --> 00:17:24,260
Hyeon Woo. I'm really sorry,

156
00:17:25,020 --> 00:17:30,260
but I could see Seul Bi's sincerity. She wanted to be with you even if it was that way.

157
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:35,170
That's why, I hope you can understand—

158
00:17:35,170 --> 00:17:37,830
Why are you telling me to understand her?

159
00:17:38,940 --> 00:17:42,300
Because of the sincerity that Seul Bi talks about,

160
00:17:42,300 --> 00:17:45,200
are you saying that my sincerity can be shattered?

161
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:49,040
No. That's not what I'm saying.

162
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:53,560
I'm tired. I want to be alone.

163
00:18:34,660 --> 00:18:38,170
Aigoo...

164
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:42,360
Aigoo, it's so hot.

165
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:45,880
♫ It's hot ♫

166
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:49,130
I told you to eat proper food instead of ramen!

167
00:18:51,420 --> 00:18:53,250
Cutie Pie!

168
00:18:56,310 --> 00:19:01,710
Thanks to this octopus porridge, you grew healthy.

169
00:19:01,710 --> 00:19:06,230
Aigoo, Ahjussi, I'm not healthy. I'm fat.

170
00:19:06,230 --> 00:19:09,760
Who said that you're fat?!

171
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:12,910
I like the way you are right now.

172
00:19:13,890 --> 00:19:16,390
Don't say that anywhere.

173
00:19:16,390 --> 00:19:18,080
I'm scared that others may hear it.

174
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:21,220
Let the whole world hear it.

175
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:25,040
Even they bring me 100 trucks-full of Go Woon,

176
00:19:25,040 --> 00:19:27,560
I won't exchange my Cutie Pie for her.

177
00:19:31,610 --> 00:19:38,960
There's only one of Seul Bi, my pretty Seul Bi, in this world.

178
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,960
You know that, right?

179
00:20:45,590 --> 00:20:48,360
<i>Jeong Won</i>

180
00:20:49,970 --> 00:20:55,340
<i>I caused a lot of trouble during all this time. Don't fight with Ye Na. Goodbye. </i>

181
00:21:14,300 --> 00:21:16,400
I was waiting for you.

182
00:21:28,550 --> 00:21:32,460
What you said was correct.

183
00:21:33,170 --> 00:21:35,930
It was me who decided

184
00:21:37,370 --> 00:21:39,140
to drink that coffee.

185
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:42,900
That's why,

186
00:21:42,900 --> 00:21:47,190
I came here to drink the coffee for the last time.

187
00:21:48,620 --> 00:21:51,080
Here. Choose one.

188
00:21:51,080 --> 00:21:54,040
Oh Go Woon's last coffee.

189
00:22:01,070 --> 00:22:04,000
<i>Americano</i>

190
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,780
I'll go with this.

191
00:22:25,010 --> 00:22:30,910
It was a really sweet dream.

192
00:22:30,910 --> 00:22:35,380
To the point, I never wanted to wake up.

193
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:45,410
Seul Bi.

194
00:22:47,770 --> 00:22:50,820
Before you start liking someone,

195
00:22:50,820 --> 00:22:54,720
make sure to love yourself first.

196
00:23:00,730 --> 00:23:04,500
God bless you.

197
00:24:01,670 --> 00:24:08,240
♫ <i>Oh, beautiful, oh</i> ♫

198
00:24:10,660 --> 00:24:17,180
♫ <i>Yeah, hey, yeah, hey, oh</i>♫

199
00:24:17,180 --> 00:24:25,760
♫ <i>With a pretty hairdo and eye-catching lipstick I wear clothes that I saved for a special day to go out</i> ♫

200
00:24:25,800 --> 00:24:32,110
♫ <i>I am excited. I am so happy</i> ♫

201
00:24:32,110 --> 00:24:40,830
♫ <i>From some point, I feel many people are staring at me</i> ♫

202
00:24:40,830 --> 00:24:47,210
♫ <i>and I like it. That makes me happy</i> ♫

203
00:24:47,210 --> 00:24:49,380
♫ <i>All day, alright</i> ♫

204
00:24:49,380 --> 00:24:52,210
♫ <i>Enjoy my life</i> ♫

205
00:24:52,210 --> 00:24:56,170
♫ <i>I'm going to run</i> ♫

206
00:24:56,170 --> 00:24:58,520
♫ <i>Yes, I'm beautiful</i> ♫

207
00:24:58,520 --> 00:25:03,510
♫ <i>I'm wonderful, today I look pretty </i> ♫

208
00:25:03,510 --> 00:25:08,200
♫ <i>Yes, so beautiful, so wonderful</i> ♫

209
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:12,320
♫ <i>Do I look pretty to everyone?</i> ♫

210
00:25:12,320 --> 00:25:17,950
♫ <i>I am feeling this happy even though you don't know about it</i> ♫

211
00:25:17,950 --> 00:25:22,240
♫ <i>Everything is perfect today</i> ♫

212
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:26,630
♫ <i>I'm a beautiful girl</i> ♫

213
00:25:29,790 --> 00:25:32,600
♫ <i>I'm still</i> ♫

214
00:25:32,600 --> 00:25:34,020
<i>Go Won, thank you for showing me your true self.</i>

215
00:25:34,020 --> 00:25:36,590
♫ <i>is a bit awkward</i> ♫

216
00:25:36,590 --> 00:25:42,380
♫ <i>I will be pretty including my spirit</i> ♫

217
00:25:42,380 --> 00:25:45,210
♫ <i>Will you take it?</i> ♫

218
00:25:55,310 --> 00:25:57,110
I'm sorry.

219
00:25:58,840 --> 00:26:00,450
For what?

220
00:26:01,610 --> 00:26:04,420
You are entitled to be angry at me for

221
00:26:04,420 --> 00:26:07,330
ignoring your feelings toward me

222
00:26:08,170 --> 00:26:10,400
this entire time.

223
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:19,510
I just came back from Dabang (Cafe).

224
00:26:21,870 --> 00:26:25,370
Did you meet Lee Seul Bi?

225
00:26:25,370 --> 00:26:26,870
Yeah.

226
00:26:29,250 --> 00:26:33,870
Jeong Won and you knew about it.

227
00:26:33,870 --> 00:26:36,370
However, although I was closer to her, I didn't know about it.

228
00:26:36,370 --> 00:26:41,360
That's because you couldn't see it because you were too close.

229
00:26:42,890 --> 00:26:48,340
Jeong Won quit his part-time job, and he can't be found

230
00:26:48,340 --> 00:26:52,110
in his practice room, at the soondae stew restaurant or playground.

231
00:26:53,760 --> 00:26:56,450
But now I see Jeong Won.

232
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:01,320
Ye Na...

233
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:08,330
You and I probably couldn't see the closest ones to us this whole time.

234
00:27:13,800 --> 00:27:15,530
I told you to eat more delicious food.

235
00:27:15,530 --> 00:27:19,990
Oh, kimbap, tteokbokki (spicy rice cake) and soondae (pork blood sausage) are the yummiest things.

236
00:27:19,990 --> 00:27:21,670
Delicious.

237
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:25,100
- Dong Goo.
- Yes?

238
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:28,590
As for the basketball manhwa you used to draw,

239
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:31,220
I think that was really interesting.

240
00:27:31,220 --> 00:27:34,080
Make sure to show it to Vice Team Leader when you're finished.

241
00:27:34,080 --> 00:27:35,800
Really?

242
00:27:35,800 --> 00:27:38,470
I thought it was a little childish.

243
00:27:38,470 --> 00:27:43,630
No. If you polish it a little bit, you will certainly be able to publish it.

244
00:27:48,040 --> 00:27:52,760
Jeong Sook, why don't you try coloring and coming up with a story?

245
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:54,230
Huh?

246
00:27:54,230 --> 00:27:58,730
You can't just draw shadows forever when you're a webtoonist.

247
00:27:59,930 --> 00:28:03,800
What's happening? You treated us to all this food and even gave us advice.

248
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:05,920
This looks like you're leaving.

249
00:28:06,730 --> 00:28:09,330
What do you mean?

250
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:13,260
I always wanted to

251
00:28:13,260 --> 00:28:17,050
treat you guys out like this.

252
00:28:17,050 --> 00:28:19,930
It's getting cold. Quickly eat it.

253
00:28:25,460 --> 00:28:26,970
Ah!

254
00:28:34,390 --> 00:28:37,110
As expected, you know a thing.

255
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:54,700
<i>Why don't you draw me?</i>

256
00:28:54,700 --> 00:28:57,990
<i>Do you also want me to draw you?</i>

257
00:29:07,210 --> 00:29:08,730
<i>Resignation</i>

258
00:29:13,900 --> 00:29:17,730
<i>Civil Servant Exam School</i>

259
00:29:17,730 --> 00:29:20,080
Hey! Fool.

260
00:29:32,650 --> 00:29:34,700
Why are you here?

261
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:38,520
I came here to see you.

262
00:29:41,850 --> 00:29:43,640
Now that you saw me, I'm leaving.

263
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:45,870
If it wasn't for you,

264
00:29:45,870 --> 00:29:48,170
only my body would have changed,

265
00:29:48,970 --> 00:29:51,720
but I wouldn't have been able to be Oh Go Woon.

266
00:29:53,630 --> 00:29:57,630
What the heck, Lee Seul Bi? You're making me feel sorry.

267
00:29:59,860 --> 00:30:03,910
I'll give you back the title of Yeonnam-dong goddess.

268
00:30:07,390 --> 00:30:10,600
Are you not going to drink the coffee anymore?

269
00:30:11,290 --> 00:30:13,050
No.

270
00:30:13,050 --> 00:30:16,570
Today is really my last day.

271
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:21,400
I'm only saying this now,

272
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:25,530
but Go Woon is ten times prettier than me.

273
00:30:25,530 --> 00:30:29,800
Of course. Not everyone can be Yeonnam-dong Goddess.

274
00:30:31,610 --> 00:30:35,290
Hey. Let's take a picture as a memory of the last time.

275
00:30:36,930 --> 00:30:40,260
Should we?

276
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:44,410
You should come closer.

277
00:30:44,410 --> 00:30:47,350
Ah, seriously...

278
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:48,580
I'm taking it.

279
00:30:48,580 --> 00:30:51,450
One, two, three.

280
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:03,680
But I like Seul Bi 100 times more.

281
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:16,560
Then, with that being said, I'm going to eat all the rice cake.

282
00:31:17,950 --> 00:31:20,240
Don't you know how much I love Korean shaved ice?

283
00:31:20,240 --> 00:31:21,930
I'm going to eat everything.

284
00:31:21,930 --> 00:31:25,960
Seriously, let's eat it together.

285
00:31:35,470 --> 00:31:37,650
How much percentage is left?

286
00:31:41,150 --> 00:31:43,470
Seventeen percent.

287
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:46,180
There's still a little bit left.

288
00:31:48,530 --> 00:31:54,000
I was always tense because I never knew when I would change back.

289
00:31:54,930 --> 00:31:57,580
I thought my heart was going to explode.

290
00:31:57,580 --> 00:32:04,090
That's what I'm saying. At night, I would always be tense and tense.

291
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:13,170
Hey. Don't you think I lost a little bit of weight after running away the entire time?

292
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:24,250
I wonder what was with these clothes that made me wanted them so much.

293
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:29,070
However, you heard my father's words, right?

294
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:33,190
He won't exchange me even for 100 trucks-full of Go Woon.

295
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:37,630
Hey! Are you going to make me sad like that?

296
00:32:37,630 --> 00:32:42,340
You got to wear all the clothes you dreamed to fit into and enjoyed all the people's attention.

297
00:32:42,340 --> 00:32:44,500
It was nice.

298
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:51,080
That's right.

299
00:32:52,430 --> 00:32:57,480
When I drank that coffee, it was exciting and fun.

300
00:33:03,170 --> 00:33:07,890
Now, it's really the last time.

301
00:33:09,140 --> 00:33:14,310
I know, right? It feels like I went on a weird vacation

302
00:33:14,310 --> 00:33:16,910
and just came back.

303
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:25,330
I'm scared again, but I'm back to my familiar body.

304
00:33:31,130 --> 00:33:36,300
Hey. Didn't you hear what Father said earlier?

305
00:33:37,190 --> 00:33:41,640
There's no one exactly like you in the world.

306
00:33:42,210 --> 00:33:48,590
One, and only one, Seul Bi exists in the world.

307
00:34:06,850 --> 00:34:09,070
Thank you, Oh Go Woon.

308
00:34:11,690 --> 00:34:18,010
You were my dream and my great friend.

309
00:34:20,590 --> 00:34:24,870
Lee Seul Bi, be well for me.

310
00:34:25,700 --> 00:34:28,470
Continue to work hard on drawing.

311
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:31,920
I got it.

312
00:34:32,510 --> 00:34:36,340
I'll be well, as myself.

313
00:35:20,700 --> 00:35:22,790
<i>Jjang-gu Appa</i>

314
00:35:44,890 --> 00:35:49,040
<i>I will wait for you on the hill</i>

315
00:36:24,230 --> 00:36:27,730
I saw your resignation.

316
00:36:27,730 --> 00:36:30,540
For not being able to stay until the very end,

317
00:36:31,410 --> 00:36:33,900
I'm truly sorry.

318
00:36:34,910 --> 00:36:41,240
Was that resignation yours or Lee Seul Bi's?

319
00:36:43,060 --> 00:36:45,330
It was Seul Bi's.

320
00:36:47,700 --> 00:36:53,530
Since Oh Go Woon won't be here anymore.

321
00:36:57,470 --> 00:37:03,630
With this appearance, I was very happy

322
00:37:05,340 --> 00:37:07,880
every moment I spent with you.

323
00:37:11,350 --> 00:37:14,720
You were happy throughout the whole time while you were tricking me?

324
00:37:19,750 --> 00:37:23,750
I don't even know now if the feelings I felt were real or fake

325
00:37:28,030 --> 00:37:32,000
when I look at you.

326
00:37:33,020 --> 00:37:36,050
I was too selfish.

327
00:37:37,550 --> 00:37:41,510
I just really liked you—

328
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:48,540
I thought I would clear up my heart if I came here, but it wasn't the case.

329
00:38:01,710 --> 00:38:08,670
This ring has no more meaning to me now.

330
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:21,910
You! How did you know I would be here?

331
00:39:21,910 --> 00:39:24,950
Your mother told me you would be here.

332
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:32,820
I wanted to look cool so I left with a memo, but my mother ruined it.

333
00:39:33,460 --> 00:39:35,870
Let me use this today.

334
00:39:44,940 --> 00:39:47,800
You always joked around with me

335
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:56,340
- about how I am a writer that writes about romance, but I've never dated anyone.
- That's right.

336
00:39:56,340 --> 00:39:59,040
However, after meeting Go Woon,

337
00:40:01,800 --> 00:40:06,980
I started having thoughts that

338
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:11,500
the drawings I drew up until now could be fake.

339
00:40:15,130 --> 00:40:18,560
I must have liked Go Woon to that extent.

340
00:40:19,090 --> 00:40:25,300
- Hyeon Woo...
- It was because I thought there would be no one in this world

341
00:40:30,010 --> 00:40:33,730
that I would open my heart to.

342
00:40:36,770 --> 00:40:39,500
I really feel like a fool.

343
00:40:45,470 --> 00:40:47,750
Ye Na is looking for you.

344
00:41:05,210 --> 00:41:10,260
Sticky, You'd better come here within five seconds.

345
00:41:11,440 --> 00:41:17,280
Five, four, three,

346
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:21,400
two, one.

347
00:41:26,530 --> 00:41:32,100
Moon Jeong Won. Why aren't you here? You're scaring me.

348
00:41:34,260 --> 00:41:37,360
Please don't be like this.

349
00:41:55,540 --> 00:41:57,990
I came back.

350
00:42:11,140 --> 00:42:15,320
You did well, Seul Bi.

351
00:42:20,820 --> 00:42:25,430
Episode 22 is done. What about episode 23?

352
00:42:25,430 --> 00:42:27,420
The background is filled up.

353
00:42:27,420 --> 00:42:29,730
I finished up the shadows, too.

354
00:42:29,730 --> 00:42:34,800
<i>I finished my part of drawing up to episode 22 and 23 where Dong Goo and Jeong Sook finished.</i>

355
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:36,490
Writer Im?

356
00:42:37,940 --> 00:42:44,030
<i>Thank you to our channel manager: _taeko10.</i>

357
00:42:45,060 --> 00:42:51,010
<i>Thank you to our English moderator: BWCatNYC.</i>

358
00:42:51,940 --> 00:42:57,970
<i>Thank you to our other language moderators and subtitlers.</i>

359
00:43:07,800 --> 00:43:10,940
<i>I'm pretty sure this is mine.</i>

360
00:43:24,520 --> 00:43:27,230
<i>My Man's Recipe</i>

361
00:43:28,990 --> 00:43:35,950
<i>Thank you to our segmenters: kitty100, pilar_velasquez, mxover, bjohnsonwong, jazmineheart hana_860, douchebag123420_701.</i>

362
00:43:36,950 --> 00:43:44,010
<i>Thank you to our Korean to English subtitlers: beccy0502, leejigeum, posi27tive, hyung123, and sophie2you.</i>

363
00:43:44,970 --> 00:43:50,950
<i>Thank you to our chief editor: Joysprite.</i>

364
00:43:52,040 --> 00:43:57,990
<i>Thank you to our translation editor: Gripstar_385.</i>

365
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:05,000
<i>Thank you to our page designer: justine_desmoulins</i>

366
00:44:06,820 --> 00:44:09,310
Hello?

367
00:44:11,670 --> 00:44:15,110
I should've done better between you guys.

368
00:44:15,110 --> 00:44:18,920
No. I am sorrier than you are.

369
00:44:18,920 --> 00:44:24,650
It wouldn't have ended like this if I listened to your words and told Writer Im back then.

370
00:44:25,480 --> 00:44:30,260
I hoped you would have had less of a hard time.

371
00:44:34,080 --> 00:44:36,810
However, did you change your phone number?

372
00:44:36,810 --> 00:44:39,550
No. I canceled my phone service.

373
00:44:39,550 --> 00:44:40,790
I'm going abroad tomorrow.

374
00:44:40,790 --> 00:44:44,050
Traveling abroad? To where?

375
00:44:44,050 --> 00:44:45,690
- New York.
- What?!

376
00:44:46,610 --> 00:44:49,150
New York is not like the next town.

377
00:44:49,150 --> 00:44:50,940
Still, you can't...

378
00:44:50,940 --> 00:44:53,790
I'm going to go to Broadway, which is the hometown of the musical,

379
00:44:53,790 --> 00:44:59,710
and I will challenge myself for the real Phantom of Opera, not that ghost of opera.

380
00:44:59,710 --> 00:45:03,650
No... should I be rooting for your decision or not?

381
00:45:05,610 --> 00:45:08,070
Does Vice Team Leader know about this?

382
00:45:08,070 --> 00:45:10,660
I don't know. I didn't tell her.

383
00:45:13,210 --> 00:45:17,340
Honestly, I got dumped by Ye Na.

384
00:45:18,040 --> 00:45:20,110
Epic.

385
00:45:20,110 --> 00:45:24,170
You and I both have strange tastes for our significant others.

386
00:45:24,170 --> 00:45:25,730
I know, right?

387
00:45:25,730 --> 00:45:30,120
Writer Im and Vice Team Leader will probably never find people like us.

388
00:45:30,120 --> 00:45:31,700
Of course not!

389
00:45:31,700 --> 00:45:36,240
Let's have a drink between people who specialize in one-sided love.

390
00:45:36,240 --> 00:45:38,060
Mr. Phantom of the Opera, cheers.

391
00:45:38,060 --> 00:45:40,400
Cheers!

392
00:45:43,350 --> 00:45:46,310
How come I feel so much more tired than usual today?

393
00:45:48,710 --> 00:45:51,170
How frustrating.

394
00:45:51,170 --> 00:45:52,270
Excuse me!

395
00:45:52,270 --> 00:45:54,690
Goo Koo.

396
00:45:56,170 --> 00:45:58,640
What did you say just now?

397
00:46:00,330 --> 00:46:05,550
Sookie, Sookie Jeong Sookie, did you draw a lot of shadows today?

398
00:46:05,550 --> 00:46:08,680
I drew a lot.

399
00:46:08,680 --> 00:46:10,390
What about our Koo Goo today?

400
00:46:10,390 --> 00:46:13,990
Today's mock test was crazy hard.

401
00:46:13,990 --> 00:46:16,660
Can you buy something to cheer me up, honey?

402
00:46:16,660 --> 00:46:17,420
Okay.

403
00:46:17,420 --> 00:46:20,000
Then drink to cheer you up. Let's go go!

404
00:46:21,490 --> 00:46:24,710
You must be very busy, right?

405
00:46:24,710 --> 00:46:28,390
Then, we'll just go on our own.

406
00:46:31,250 --> 00:46:34,310
What should we eat?

407
00:46:42,580 --> 00:46:45,360
Ra Ra

408
00:46:47,350 --> 00:46:49,810
Vice Team Leader Kang, we got the first snow.

409
00:46:49,810 --> 00:46:52,030
Let's eat it together to celebrate. I got some food.

410
00:46:52,030 --> 00:46:54,850
Don't use slang. It doesn't suit you well.

411
00:46:54,850 --> 00:46:56,100
No thanks.

412
00:46:56,100 --> 00:46:58,970
Since you keep eating salad or drinking coffee,

413
00:46:58,970 --> 00:47:01,810
you're getting more snappish.

414
00:47:01,810 --> 00:47:05,870
You look like you will pass away at any time.

415
00:47:05,870 --> 00:47:09,320
Perhaps, did you get dumped by a guy?

416
00:47:10,080 --> 00:47:11,570
Dumped? Who got dumped?!

417
00:47:11,570 --> 00:47:15,130
Why are you upset? As if you really got dumped by someone.

418
00:47:15,130 --> 00:47:18,750
It's scary. It's scary. Vice Team Leader Kang is scary.

419
00:47:20,750 --> 00:47:23,240
Take back any affection you have towards me.

420
00:47:23,240 --> 00:47:25,820
You go and eat the chicken by yourselves.

421
00:47:25,820 --> 00:47:26,990
Do whatever you want. Okay?!

422
00:47:26,990 --> 00:47:29,810
Geez, how snappish.

423
00:47:40,600 --> 00:47:42,750
Lee Seul Bi?

424
00:47:48,030 --> 00:47:50,990
The owner of this coffee finally came.

425
00:47:52,030 --> 00:47:54,290
I've been waiting for you.

426
00:47:55,990 --> 00:48:02,270
You must really be God.

427
00:48:02,270 --> 00:48:06,590
Stop the obvious talk and quickly drink it.

428
00:48:17,520 --> 00:48:19,070
It's tasty.

429
00:48:19,070 --> 00:48:20,960
Right?

430
00:48:20,960 --> 00:48:25,680
Seul Bi also told me that my coffee is impeccable.

431
00:48:25,680 --> 00:48:30,740
Do you know what type of people drink the magical coffee?

432
00:48:30,740 --> 00:48:35,850
People who desperately want to be loved.

433
00:48:36,890 --> 00:48:38,550
Just like Seul Bi.

434
00:48:38,550 --> 00:48:42,570
I gave choices to Seul Bi constantly.

435
00:48:42,570 --> 00:48:47,660
If you want to love, you have to love yourself first.

436
00:48:49,140 --> 00:48:51,490
But it wasn't the case for Seul Bi.

437
00:48:52,590 --> 00:48:58,250
Then, do you also know the end result?

438
00:48:58,250 --> 00:49:04,990
People who recognized true sincerity beyond outer appearance found the love.

439
00:49:04,990 --> 00:49:09,690
People who couldn't see that failed in love.

440
00:49:09,690 --> 00:49:12,100
Well, it's a long story.

441
00:49:12,100 --> 00:49:18,070
What I'm saying is each love is different, just like each person is different.

442
00:49:21,960 --> 00:49:26,440
I drank the coffee well.

443
00:49:57,780 --> 00:49:59,610
Sticky!

444
00:50:05,880 --> 00:50:07,280
Ye Na.

445
00:50:07,280 --> 00:50:09,650
What the heck is wrong with you?

446
00:50:09,650 --> 00:50:11,530
How did you know I would be here?

447
00:50:11,530 --> 00:50:15,440
Lee Seul Bi told me that you'll be going to the USA.

448
00:50:18,940 --> 00:50:22,720
It really is hard to leave while looking cool.

449
00:50:22,720 --> 00:50:25,140
Where are you going to America?

450
00:50:26,190 --> 00:50:30,220
To have an audition for Broadway.

451
00:50:30,930 --> 00:50:33,190
Broadway?!

452
00:50:35,130 --> 00:50:37,960
What can I do with you?!

453
00:50:39,100 --> 00:50:43,330
I need to go. I'm going to miss the flight time.

454
00:50:46,270 --> 00:50:48,230
Just stay here.

455
00:50:48,230 --> 00:50:52,630
Don't go to America and just do it here, in Korea.

456
00:50:56,520 --> 00:51:01,830
It doesn't matter to you where I go.

457
00:51:12,940 --> 00:51:17,340
How can you just confess to me and end it on your own?

458
00:51:18,190 --> 00:51:19,770
What?

459
00:51:21,590 --> 00:51:24,840
If it bothers me that much, then I should take responsibility. You told me that.

460
00:51:24,840 --> 00:51:29,810
So! I'm telling you to just stay by my side, you fool.

461
00:51:33,630 --> 00:51:36,790
♫ Right now, in this moment ♫

462
00:51:36,790 --> 00:51:37,520
Hey..

463
00:51:37,520 --> 00:51:41,110
♫ My everything... ♫

464
00:52:03,410 --> 00:52:04,710
What's with the two of you?

465
00:52:04,710 --> 00:52:09,140
Im Hyeon Woo, please lend the studio to my Jeong Won.

466
00:52:10,230 --> 00:52:13,310
She called him, "my Jeong Won" instead of Sticky.

467
00:52:13,310 --> 00:52:15,060
Is this real?

468
00:52:15,060 --> 00:52:20,600
No. It's because my Ye Na said she can't stand being away from me even for a sec.

469
00:52:20,600 --> 00:52:22,840
I'll just try out for Broadway next year.

470
00:52:22,840 --> 00:52:25,880
Don't even think about going to Broadway from now on.

471
00:52:25,880 --> 00:52:27,490
Okay.

472
00:52:28,890 --> 00:52:31,320
Go and do some facial mask packs.

473
00:52:31,320 --> 00:52:34,390
Brace yourself to practice a lot.

474
00:52:34,390 --> 00:52:37,240
Ye Na. Come quickly.

475
00:52:37,240 --> 00:52:39,630
Okay.

476
00:52:41,730 --> 00:52:45,580
You two should help my Jeong Won out, too.

477
00:52:46,740 --> 00:52:49,430
Let's talk.

478
00:52:49,430 --> 00:52:51,130
Yeah.

479
00:52:57,490 --> 00:53:00,490
Are you two really dating now?

480
00:53:01,130 --> 00:53:05,230
What choice do I have? I should take care of him.

481
00:53:05,230 --> 00:53:09,510
So, you don't have to feel sorry for me anymore.

482
00:53:09,510 --> 00:53:11,410
Alright.

483
00:53:12,200 --> 00:53:17,400
However, what do you like about Jeong Won?

484
00:53:17,400 --> 00:53:21,290
I'm most comfortable with him, and he knows about me the most.

485
00:53:22,810 --> 00:53:26,480
You should go quickly. He's probably waiting for you.

486
00:53:28,560 --> 00:53:34,450
Take a close look at "Let's Meet at 11 O'clock" because Seul Bi left something there for you.

487
00:53:51,060 --> 00:53:55,680
<i>However, if I had a different appearance</i>

488
00:53:55,680 --> 00:54:02,250
<i>would we still be like this?</i>

489
00:54:12,220 --> 00:54:17,740
<i>People who recognized true sincerity beyond outer appearance found love.</i>

490
00:54:17,740 --> 00:54:22,160
<i>People who couldn't see that failed in love.</i>

491
00:54:40,550 --> 00:54:42,750
Writer Im...

492
00:54:46,250 --> 00:54:49,810
Although I said the outside appearance wasn't important,

493
00:54:51,520 --> 00:54:54,390
I didn't mean it.

494
00:54:55,680 --> 00:54:57,510
I acknowledge it.

495
00:55:02,620 --> 00:55:11,510
However, the reason I liked Go Woon

496
00:55:15,350 --> 00:55:17,800
was all about you.

497
00:55:17,800 --> 00:55:20,130
<i>Writer Im Hyeon Woo.</i>

498
00:55:20,130 --> 00:55:22,200
<i>Hey, you bastard!</i>

499
00:55:22,200 --> 00:55:26,600
